---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Stairlift & Ramp Repair | Service & Maintenance Rochester Buffalo Syracuse NY"
  description="Expert repair and maintenance for stairlifts, ramps and vertical lifts from all brands in Rochester, Buffalo and Syracuse NY. Fast local service. Call (585) 488-0771."
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <nav class="text-sm mb-6 text-slate-500">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-slate-700">Home</a> <span class="mx-1">/</span> 
      <span class="text-slate-700">Service</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter mb-6">Service &amp; Repair</h1>

    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600">
        From unsafe stairs to ramps needing repair, our team of skilled technicians is here to help! 
        Whether it’s an indoor or outdoor stairlift, ramp, or lift from any manufacturer, Freedom Mobility NY stands ready to assist.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-8">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-4">We service all major brands</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-1">
          <a href="https://ameriglide.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">AmeriGlide</a>
          <a href="https://www.harmar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Harmar</a>
          <a href="https://www.bruno.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Bruno</a>
          <a href="https://www.stannah.com/stairlifts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Stannah</a>
          <a href="https://www.acornstairlifts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Acorn</a>
          <a href="https://www.handicare.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Handicare</a>
          <a href="https://www.savaria.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Savaria</a>
          <a href="https://www.garaventa.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-sky-600 hover:underline">Garaventa</a>
          <div class="col-span-2 text-xs text-slate-500 pt-1">+ most other manufacturers</div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm"><a href="/brands" class="text-sky-600 hover:underline font-medium">View our full list of brands &amp; partners →</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-8 border">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">Common services</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Annual safety inspections &amp; tune-ups</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Battery &amp; charger replacement</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Rail, seat, and motor repairs</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Ramp surface &amp; structure fixes</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Lift platform &amp; gate repairs</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="font-mono text-emerald-500">→</span> Emergency service available</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="tel:5854880771" class="mt-5 block text-sm font-semibold text-sky-600">Call for service: (585) 488-0771</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <div class="uppercase text-sky-400 tracking-widest text-xs mb-1">IS YOUR EQUIPMENT SLOW OR MAKING NOISE?</div>
        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Schedule a service call with our Mobility Specialist today.</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <a href="/contact" class="whitespace-nowrap bg-white text-slate-900 px-8 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold inline-block">Request Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Internal Linking: Locations for this service -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Service & Repair Available in These Areas</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm">
      <a href="/locations/rochester/service" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Service in Rochester, NY →</a>
      <a href="/locations/buffalo/service" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Service in Buffalo, NY →</a>
      <a href="/locations/syracuse/service" class="p-4 border rounded hover:bg-slate-50">Service in Syracuse, NY →</a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">We also serve surrounding communities. <a href="/locations" class="underline">View all locations</a>.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ for Featured Snippets -->
  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6">Frequently Asked Questions About Mobility Equipment Service</h2>
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">How much does stairlift or ramp repair cost in Rochester, Buffalo or Syracuse?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Service costs depend on the issue and equipment brand. Many repairs start at a few hundred dollars. We provide transparent quotes and offer 18-month Gold Star warranties on new installations.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">Do you service equipment from other companies?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Yes. Our technicians repair and maintain stairlifts, ramps and lifts from <a href="https://ameriglide.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">AmeriGlide</a>, <a href="https://www.harmar.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Harmar</a>, <a href="https://www.bruno.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Bruno</a>, <a href="https://www.stannah.com/stairlifts/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Stannah</a>, <a href="https://www.acornstairlifts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline">Acorn</a> and most other major manufacturers across Western and Central New York.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
        <summary class="font-medium cursor-pointer">How quickly can you respond for emergency service?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">We prioritize emergency calls in the Rochester, Buffalo and Syracuse areas and can often schedule same or next-day service depending on the issue and location.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How much does stairlift or ramp repair cost in Rochester, Buffalo or Syracuse?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Service costs depend on the issue and equipment brand. Many repairs start at a few hundred dollars. We provide transparent quotes and offer 18-month Gold Star warranties on new installations."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "Do you service equipment from other companies?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Yes. Our technicians repair and maintain stairlifts, ramps and lifts from AmeriGlide, Harmar, Bruno, Stannah, Acorn and most other major manufacturers across Western and Central New York."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How quickly can you respond for emergency service?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "We prioritize emergency calls in the Rochester, Buffalo and Syracuse areas and can often schedule same or next-day service depending on the issue and location."
        }
      }
    ]
  })} />
</Layout>
